David West has matched his season-high with 10 points, recording his third double-digit scoring game of the season.
Patrick McCaw has hit three three-pointers tonight (3-of-4 3FG), tying a career-high for three-pointers made in a game.
Andre Iguodala has matched his season-high with eight free throws tonight.
Warriors outscored the Hawks 33-24 in the third quarter and enter the final frame with a 94-90 lead. BOX SCORE:pic.twitter.com/pvg2keAuin

Draymond Green has extended his career-best streak of games with at least one steal to 22-straight.
Warriors dished out 18 helpers on 20 made baskets in the first half, assisting on 90% of their field goals.
Ian Clark is in double figures for the 12th time this season. He has 10 points in seven minutes at the half.
At the half, Warriors trail the Hawks 66-61. Andre Iguodala has a team-high 14 points. BOX SCORE:pic.twitter.com/bNvDGUqeQD
